data.description: Discover the charm of this delightful Cape Cod home nestled at the end of a peaceful cul-de-sac. This home has been meticulously maintained, ensuring it is in excellent condition for its next lucky owner. The bright and welcoming eat-in kitchen is perfect for enjoying meals with loved ones or peaceful meals alone. The convenience of a first-floor primary bedroom offers ease of living, providing a comfortable retreat just steps away from the main living areas. The beautifully landscaped entryway adds to the curb appeal and sets a welcoming tone for all who enter.  Enjoy your own private oasis in the backyard, a place where you can relax, entertain, or simply soak up the tranquility.  This home's location is ideal, offering easy access to nearby interstates, making your daily commute and errands a breeze. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful property your new home!
